530
00:36:53,211 --> 00:36:54,269
The bus will leave in the
morning at 6 o'clock.

531
00:37:00,551 --> 00:37:03,486
Are you feeling sleepy?
- No! What about you?

532
00:37:11,562 --> 00:37:16,295
