585
00:41:51,909 --> 00:41:54,901
On opening the eyes, slumber says.

586
00:41:54,979 --> 00:41:58,574
What fervour is this?

587
00:41:59,984 --> 00:42:03,112
Here and there. God knows where.

588
00:42:03,187 --> 00:42:06,918
This fervour is taking me.

589
00:42:07,791 --> 00:42:15,664
Come. We will find
a way in this world.

